<template>
  <GChart type="PieChart" :data="chartData" :options="chartOptions" />
</template>
      
      <script>
import { GChart } from "vue-google-charts";

export default {
  name: "GoogleChart",
  components: {
    GChart,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      chartData: [["Age", "Weight"], [12], [5.5], [14], [5], [3.5], [7]],

      chartOptions: {
        legend: "none",
        is3D: true,
        // pieSliceText: "none",
        height: 600,

        backgroundColor: "rgb(154, 155, 157)",

        slices: {
          4: { offset: 0.3 },
          9: { offset: 0.1 },
          6: { offset: 0.4 },
          5: { offset: 0.5 },
        },
      },
    };
  },
};
</script>
